                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4605" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0670</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8373 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四两拨千斤，可有千斤力在后？——抚顺特钢债务重整之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Way of Fushun Special Steel Co. Debt Consolidation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘亚莉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">抚顺特钢</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">债务重整；债转股；资本结构；债务豁免；营业外收入</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">debt consolidation; debt-equity swap; capital structure; debt forgiveness; non-operating income</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业普遍存在资产负债率高的问题。抚顺特钢是我国大型特殊钢重点企业和军工材料研发及生产基地，2018年公司因巨额债务无法按期清偿引发重大财务风险，并因“连续两年亏损且最近一年期末净资产为负”被证监会实施退市风险警示。本案例描述了抚顺特钢通过债转股手段去杠杆进行资本结构优化的过程。公司通过控股股东捐赠、资本公积转增资本、股权抵偿债权的方式，以极低代价实施了债转股重整方案，重整过程中的债务豁免则作为债务重整利得归属于营业外收入使公司2018年成功扭亏为盈。抚顺特钢妥善化解了财务风险与退市风险两大危机，彻底改善了公司的资本结构。但债务重整仅仅解决了抚顺特钢的燃眉之急，产品毛利率低下仍是影响企业未来发展的关键不利因素，抚顺特钢要实现凤凰涅槃还任重道远。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">There is a general problem of high financial leverage in the iron and steel industry. Fushun Special Steel is a large-scale special steel key enterprise and military material R&amp;D and manufacturing base in China. In 2018, the company is facing two crises: one is failing to pay off its huge debts on schedule which causes significant financial risks; the other is being warned of delisting risks by the CSRC due to &quot;two consecutive years of losses and negative net assets at the end of the latest year&quot;. This case describes the process of capital structure optimization of Fushun Special Steel through debt-equity swap. The company implemented debt-equity swap plan at extremely low cost by means of donations from controlling shareholders, capital reserves converted into capital and equity to repay creditor&#39;s rights. The debt restructuring gains generated by debt exemption also turned the company into profit in 2018. Fushun Special Steel has properly solved the two major crises of financial risk and delisting risk, and thoroughly improved the capital structure of the company. However, the debt restructuring only solved the urgent problem of Fushun Special Steel, the low gross profit rate of products and other problems have not been reversed, and the enterprise still has a long way to go to maintain its sustainable operation ability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《财务管理》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业财务困境、上市公司债务重整方式选择、营业外收入对企业盈利能力的影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
